review:
Strongly recommend Dr. Dolly to anyone looking for Quality, Painless and long term solution for your teeth! She is technically sound, detail oriented and explains the issue really well. No unnecessary procedure if not required. She is one of the best in the industry and what adds to the positive experience is her friendly and calm demeanor and patience while you explain your problem.
Thanks for the great experience. Never thought visiting a dentist can be so pleasant:) Best wishes to her !!
